      "content": "idk im just really overwhelmed with everything... i dont have time to go to a hospital right now and it's so expensive here. i feel like i'm just spiraling because of the flight delay and the heat. would trying some deep breathing exercises or maybe just taking a sedative help me calm down so this feeling goes away?",
